room_text:
Well well well. Not sure how you ended up here... but it looks like 
you got yourself into a sticky situation.

No worries. There is a way out of here: 

Take whatever money you have in your pocket, and go forward into any
of these honeycomb rooms that are accessible.

Here, take this deck of cards. You'll need it. 
You can keep that... I don't want it after you touched it...

Each room has a host bee that you must win a simple game of highest
card against to proceed. Aces are high, no Jokers. The closer you get
to the Queen (I'll get into her whole deal in a second), the worse
your odds are of winning, because they are straight up cheaters, and
the higher-ups play with only partial decks. (I heard the top bees
play only with Jacks, Queens, Kings and Aces...)  

If the situation does not seem favorable to you, you may run away, 
but at a cost. See, humans don't know this but our stingers hurt you
based on your bond with each individual bee. We have a straight wire
tap to the Love API that tells us how much we'll hurt you. So if you
run away, we'll sting you! But the amount of health you'll lose will 
be based off our very advanced proprietary calculations from that API

Once you get passed a room, you can't go back in... Unless you run
into that pushy sales bee... I think he has a way to unlock rooms. 
So pick your path wisely just in case.

Take this device with you. Every bee has one to navigate around here.
It's a HONEYCOMB-TRONIC VIEWER 3000! Wow, they give guests the 3000s?
... mine's only a 1800C. Anyway! This thing shows you where you're at 
right now in the middle of the screen, and shows the adjacent rooms 
you can go to (or not, if they're grayed out). It also shows your 
health and your cash on hand. As well as your current location label
on the rightmost square there. And oh ya, the honey indicator...

So uh, the only way you'll get out of here is if you give the Queen
500K units of honey, or more. She'll take it all. Our honey is worth
whatever the BEE crypto coin is worth (don't ask), so whatever cash on
hand you have will get converted to BEE coins in real time, which to
us is the same as honey. Get it? The honey value on your device there 
is based on the current exchange rate. If that's below 500K be careful
when you go see the Queen. She'll probably sting you if you don't have
enough... But hey, maybe you'll be a good match with the Love API and 
it won't hurt!

I think that's about it... Oh, if you spot any cash on the ground, its
all yours. It's probably from the last person who got stung to death! 

Good luck!
I might "bee" small, but I know how to put a card down, sucka!
Bee-hold! A fool who wants to gamble my honey!
Listen, I don't even want to "bee" here. Let's just get this over with.
Bzzt bzzt, buzzidy buzz buzz buzzeroo. Buzz!
Well hello there good lookin'. Care to play? No puns here, honey.

Don't "bee" scared. Bee-neath this rough exterior there's a kind
and gentle bee-ing.
I heard you were coming. "Bee" ready to "bee", uhm … carded!
Beets, beets, beets, beets, beets, beets, beets, beets. Beets!
Howdy doody stranger. Do you think I'm bee-utiful ? Huh!? How dare you!

Lets do this! Come on! Lets go! Alright! I'm ready! Woohoo!
Too much coffee?! Never!!

You're about halfway there. How are you feeling? Want to take a nap?
Too bad!

My boss says I have to think of something clever to say but I'm not
in the mood. Bee-gone soon please.

Oh this is my moment! Okay put your cards where you mouth is, friend.
What do you got?

Can you hear her buzzing? The Queen… You better make her happy.
We don't like when she's unhappy.

Well g'day good sir and or madam. How may I be of service to you?
Cheerio, let us partake in this exchange shall we? Mmm, yes. I do bee-lieve.
Bzzzzt buzz buzz, man! Bzzzt buzz buzzing ya know, bro?

I'm like, SUPER smart. If I really wanted to, I could "bee"t you at
this game, but it just wouldn't "bee" fair to you.

You're in the upper tier now. Want me to put you out of your misery?
You need to make her happy… the Queen Bee, you see?
Bee-hind every good bee there's always a stinger. (I'm here all week)
Put the card down. Or don't. See what happens.

Bee-cause of you, the Queen tells us to be on our best behaviour.
Can you bee-lieve that? What about our feelings?

You got any VHS tapes lying around?? I need them. I have a V-Bee-R
(a video bee recorder) and I'm itching to use it!

My mom thinks I'm special. Bee-cause I could count to ten bee-fore
I turned 3 hours old. It helps with these card games.

WHO ARE YOU? WHERE AM I? HELLO? Oh, light switch. There we go.
Hello! Oh god... Let me turn that light back off, one second.
Okay, what's up?

Not much further now. Do you have what she wants? You better have
what she wants…

I have a Justin Bee-ber concert to attend, so if we can make this
quick that'd be great.
You'll have to go through me first, buddy! Buzz buzz, mudabuzzer!

There's no turning back now. Or maybe there is… Not sure. That's what
your map is for. What am I, your Bee Guide? Buzz off.

Buuuzzzzzzzz! You made it. I hope my minions weren't too, beeeee… uh…
bee… loved? Beeloved? No no. Too, bee-gg on, uh, hurting you! Bzz
bzz bzz. So, do you have what I demand?

Oh no… They killed you? That's unfortunate. Well, we're always here
if you want to come back for more sweet sweet justice!

Hello there stranger. Are you hurt? Let me heal you. It will only
cost you a little…

Oh there's the gambling outsider! Let me sell you something, I've
got a deal you won't "bee"lieve!
